The paper discusses deep reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). The focus is on robotic control tasks, specifically self-driving vehicles, which falls under robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY). The paper also mentions the use of policy networks, which are commonly used in computer vision (cs.CV) for tasks such as image classification.
